Package com.secres

Class View

java.lang.Object
com.secres.View
public class View
extends Object
View creates and initializes the whole GUI of the Main application.
The GUI uses standard Swing components with nested JPanels. The main layout used is CardLayout for an MDI with easy visualization.

There are two JTables each with their own dataset. GraphCharts reads from the tables for the visualization.

All of View's components are accessed on the EDT per Swing's threading rules.

Author:
Pranav Amarnath
